Chicken Legs

Ingredients:
    Chicken Leg x2
    Salt 3g
    Chili Pepper 3g
    Tomato x1
Steps:
    Season Each Chicken Leg With:
        Salt 3g
        Chili Pepper 3g

    Slice
        Tomato x1 (Gives Tomato Slices x1)

    Grill
        Chicken Leg x2(Each Side)
        Tomato Slices x1

    Transfer to Plate
        Chicken Leg x2
        Tomato Slices x1

    Serve Hot